<table width="auto"  border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0"><tr><td colspan=3>House Bill/Resolution NO. <b>HB00130</b></td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>FULL TITLE : AN ACT PROVIDING COMPENSATION FOR BARANGAY OFFICIALS, AMENDING SECTION 393 OF REPUBLIC ACT NO. 7160, OTHERWISE KNOWN AS ꞌTHE LOCAL GOVERNMENT CODE OF 1991ꞌ, AND APPROPRIATING FUNDS THEREFOR</td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>ABSTRACT : Provides the following monthly compensation, in addition to benefits provided by Law, for Barangays Officials:
a.) P12,000 for the Punong Barangay
b.) P8,000 for the seven (7) Sangguniang Barangay Members
c.) P6,000 for the Barangay Secretary 
d.) P6,000 for the Barangay Treasurer
e.) P2,000 for every Member of the Lupong Tagapamayapa, Barangay Health Workers, and the Barangay Tanods
</td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>PRINCIPAL AUTHOR/S : <b>ZUBIRI, MANUEL F.</b></td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>DATE FILED : 2019-07-01</td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>SIGNIFICANCE: NATIONAL</td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>CO-AUTHORS (Journal Entries) :</td></tr><tr><td>1. Sy-Alvarado (000 2019-09-13)</td><td>2. Dalipe (000 2020-02-10)</td><tr><td>3. Olivarez (000 2020-02-13)</td><tr><td colspan=3><b>ACTIONS TAKEN BY THE COMMITTEE ON RULES</b></td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>REFERRAL TO THE COMMITTEE ON LOCAL GOVERNMENT ON 2019-07-23</td></tr></table>